headline: Morgan Stanley Investment Management Provides $125 Million Debt Financing to FreshBooks
summary: NEW YORK, March 20, 2025--Morgan Stanley Investment Management announced today that funds managed by Morgan Stanley Expansion Capital and Morgan Stanley Private Credit have provided $125 million in senior debt financing to FreshBooks, one of the leaders in cloud-based accounting software for small businesses. This investment will refinance existing debt and is expected to fuel the company’s continued growth.
